00:55:19,767 --> 00:55:21,132
For what ?

676
00:55:21,202 --> 00:55:23,193
Things I did.

677
00:55:24,873 --> 00:55:27,364
I wasn't married
when I had my baby.

678
00:55:29,344 --> 00:55:31,778
Do you really think
this is what you deserve ?

679
00:55:34,082 --> 00:55:36,573
<i>Let me tell you about</i>
<i>what you deserve, Novalee.</i>

680
00:55:36,651 --> 00:55:40,087
- If it were up to me--
<i>- [ Siren Wailing ]</i>

681
00:55:46,194 --> 00:55:49,561
[ Wailing Continues ]

682
00:55:54,569 --> 00:55:57,265
<i>- [ Truck Doors Close ]</i>
<i>- [ Engine Starts ]</i>

683
00:55:58,406 --> 00:56:01,500
<i>[ Dispatcher, Indistinct ]</i>

684
00:56:04,379 --> 00:56:07,678
Sorry, folks. We got a classical
crime scene across the street.

685
00:56:07,749 --> 00:56:09,842
- Oh, my God !
- You can't--
- Let her go !

686
00:56:09,918 --> 00:56:12,819
Hey, hey, hey !
Get down !

687
00:56:12,887 --> 00:56:15,583
- Hey !
<i>- [ Sirens Wailing ]</i>

688
00:56:15,657 --> 00:56:18,125
[ Tires Screech ]

689
00:56:19,427 --> 00:56:22,919
[ Gasping ]

690
00:56:22,997 --> 00:56:24,931
<i>[ Sirens Stop ]</i>

691
00:56:38,646 --> 00:56:40,580
[ Baby Fussing ]

692
00:56:46,354 --> 00:56:49,915
[ Crying ]

693
00:56:49,991 --> 00:56:52,152
[ Laughing ]

694
00:56:52,226 --> 00:56:56,492
A highway patrol had spotted
a Mississippi plate and stopped 'em.

695
00:56:56,564 --> 00:57:00,022
They admitted they took her and
said we'd find her right here.

696
00:57:00,101 --> 00:57:03,161
[ Continues Crying ]

697
00:57:25,426 --> 00:57:30,056
Jesus Christ. Another guitar player.
What's your name ?

698
00:57:30,131 --> 00:57:32,099
WillyJack Pickens.

699
00:57:32,166 --> 00:57:35,363
You didn't even
have to make that up did you ?

700
00:57:35,436 --> 00:57:36,835
What ?

701
00:57:36,904 --> 00:57:39,532
Well, you just carry that guitar
around to keep your balance ?

702
00:57:39,607 --> 00:57:41,837
You want me to play ?

703
00:57:41,909 --> 00:57:44,707
What the fuck do you think
I want you to do, call bingo ?

704
00:57:46,748 --> 00:57:50,206
One, two. You're best shot.

705
00:57:50,284 --> 00:57:53,378
All right.
Well, I wrote this one myself.

706
00:57:53,454 --> 00:57:57,413
- I have goose bumps already.
-Jesus Christ.

707
00:57:57,492 --> 00:58:02,259
<i>[ Guitar ]</i>

